# Classical text ciphers: Caesar (case-preserving, mod-26 wrap),
# ROT13 (self-inverse), Vigenere (LEMON+ATTACKATDAWN=LXFOPVEFRNHR
# is the textbook example), Atbash (A<->Z self-inverse).
# Non-letter chars pass through; non-letter key  <NULL>.
DEF
ABC
Khoor, Zruog!
ABC
Hello, World!
ABC
Uryyb, Jbeyq!
Hello, World!
LXFOPVEFRNHR
ATTACKATDAWN
Rijvs, Uyvjn!
<NULL>
<NULL>
SVOOL
Hello, World!
Hello
